fields.Title: SEAFORT INT / FELD INSULAR CONSOLE
fields.Description: old electronic console â€“ turn on lights and open blast door if fuel in generator

fields.Title: Encyclopedia: "It's an air-gapped system. An *off-..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It's an air-gapped system. An *off-air* military model. Its circuits are nearly impossible to *bend*, i.e. it cannot be remote controlled.

fields.Title: Feld "Insular" Console: "The dial slides under the dusty gla..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The dial slides under the dusty glass, dark and silent despite the power being on. You make out defunct stations on the UKV frequency. The words "FELD INSULAR" are written on the band.

fields.Title: You: ""What's there?" (Point to the door...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What's there?" (Point to the door.)

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Extra good that I do.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Extra good that I do."

fields.Title: Perception (Sight): "Pollen drifts in the light shaft."
fields.Dialogue Text: Pollen drifts in the light shaft.

fields.Title: You: ""Wait, what about this fuel I found..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Wait, what about this fuel I found from my MC?" (Show him the canister.)

fields.Title: You: "What does it... *do*?"
fields.Dialogue Text: What does it... *do*?

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: Variable["seafort.blast_interfacing_open_big_one"] == false  and  Variable["TASK.open_blast_door"] == false  and  Variable["TASK.open_blast_door_done"] == false  and  Variable["TASK.fuel_the_generator_done"] == false

fields.Title: You: "[Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: [Leave.]

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Electrical devices do not work wit..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Electrical devices do not work without electricity." The lieutenant looks on as you fiddle with the dial. "We need to power the generator upstairs first."

fields.Title: Feld "Insular" Console: "Who's to say this thing even works?..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Who's to say this thing even works? You have to supply it with power first. There must be a generator nearby.
fields.Alternate1: Who's to say this thing even works? You will have to provide it with power first. There was an un-fuelled generator upstairs...

fields.Title: Interfacing: "The boat engine!"
fields.Dialogue Text: The boat engine!

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I don't know.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't know."

fields.Title: You: ""I'm scared.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm scared."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno doesn't know, but Cuno wants..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno doesn't know, but Cuno wants to know."

fields.Title: You: ""Don't worry, kid. I'm a cop. Maybe..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Don't worry, kid. I'm a cop. Maybe I don't have a gun, but I'm a cop."

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: Variable["seafort.console_cuno_spooky_place"]  and  CheckItem("gun_ruby") == false  and  CheckItem("gun_villiers") == false

fields.Title: Feld "Insular" Console: "Green paint flakes off the monobloc..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Green paint flakes off the monoblock aluminium cabinet. There are rows of switches on the front panel, a frequency band and even a keyboard...

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""The console of an antique computat..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "The console of an antique computation device." The lieutenant points to the wires running into the machine. "There was a generator upstairs, with wires coming out. They terminate here."

fields.Title: Logic: "You're right. You're not a *circuit..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You're right. You're not a *circuit bender*. You don't know about these things.

fields.Title: You: "[Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: [Leave.]

fields.Title: Perception (Sight): "Pollen drifts in the light shaft."
fields.Dialogue Text: Pollen drifts in the light shaft.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""This is an air-gapped system." The..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "This is an air-gapped system." The lieutenant inspects the indicator. "*Off-air,* I think they call it. That won't work."

fields.Title: You: "Nod in agreement."
fields.Dialogue Text: Nod in agreement.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Don't be. I have a gun." He takes..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Don't be. I have a gun." He takes out his sidearm, checks the barrel, then holsters it again.

fields.Title: Half Light: "A sudden wave of anxiety makes your..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A sudden wave of anxiety makes your skin crawl.

fields.Title: Half Light: "A sudden anxious fear makes your sk..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A sudden anxious fear makes your skin crawl.

fields.Title: You: "Maybe I could contact Soona -- the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Maybe I could contact Soona -- the programmer lady? She could open the door remotely...
fields.Alternate1: "Maybe we could contact Soona -- the programmer lady? She could open the door for us remotely."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""No, I'm not, but it would not be v..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "No, I'm not, but it would not be very good military technology if programmer ladies could control it remotely. Also, it's ancient. Incompatible."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""So did I. Not back there, but... I..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "So did I. Not back there, but... I've felt it since we came here."

fields.Title: You: ""Let's go." [Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: "Let's go." [Leave.]

fields.Title: You: "Nah, it won't work. The canister fe..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Nah, it won't work. The canister feels light.

fields.Title: Feld "Insular" Console: "The glass is dusty, it's hard to ma..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The glass is dusty, it's hard to make out the writing on the band. Nothing has changed about it.

fields.Title: Interfacing: "Automatic boot."
fields.Dialogue Text: Automatic boot.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Old hardware." He points to the wi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Old hardware." He points to the wires running into the machine. "From the big power-box upstairs. Circuit-bender shit. Military-grade."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""There's barely anything left. That..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "There's barely anything left. That won't work."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Aw shit, it's on..." He grins. "Tu..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Aw shit, it's on..." He grins. "Turn: Emergency -- Open!"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""'Urgence -- Ouvert!', 'Allumer', '..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "'Urgence -- Ouvert!', 'Allumer', 'RadiodiffusÃ©'." He inspects the dials. "Sounds like this device was used to control the electronics here. Maybe it still does?"

fields.Title: Interfacing: "This device was used to control the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This device was used to control the electronics in the room. It could open doors, control lights, function as a radiocomputer...

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I think yes. Let's see..." He poin..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I think yes. Let's see..." He points to the emergency dial switch. "That one. The emergency open..."

fields.Title: You: ""Let's go." [Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: "Let's go." [Leave.]

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Whoa... Told you. Military mega gr..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Whoa... Told you. Military mega grade. Also, like, four hundred years old, I think? A thousand?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Why? The door is open -- we can ju..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Why? The door is open -- we can just fuck on now."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Fucking great. Spooky island shit..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Fucking great. Spooky island shit is gonna shit on us and we can't even *shoot* it."

fields.Title: You: "(Peek into the canister.)"
fields.Dialogue Text: (Peek into the canister.)

fields.Title: Feld "Insular" Console: "The keys rattle like teeth. This ke..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The keys rattle like teeth. This keyboard hasn't been functional in decades.

fields.Title: Feld "Insular" Console: "A dim golden glow animates the cons..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A dim golden glow animates the console. Faint, like a ghost-light. 'Urgence -- Ouvert!' reads one dial key. 'Allumer', reads another.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""No, no, no..." He stares at you as..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "No, no, no..." He stares at you as you fiddle with the dial. "We gotta juice this thing first. Power it up! Pow-pow-power it up, get it?"

fields.Title: You: ""Okay.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""INSULAR..." The lieutenant leans i..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "INSULAR..." The lieutenant leans in to inspect the cursive writing. "This is an *off-air* radiocomputer, I believe. Used for military communications."

fields.Title: Logic: "Wait, actually, this would not be v..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Wait, actually, this would not be very good military technology if *programmer ladies* could control it remotely... It's probably not connected to the front. Or just plain broken. Nice idea, though...

fields.Title: Feld "Insular" Console: "With the door open, the dial switch..."
fields.Dialogue Text: With the door open, the dial switch has locked into place -- a security measure of some sort.

fields.Title: Shivers: "A thin wisp of smoke rises from a c..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A thin wisp of smoke rises from a charred black firepit... the wind picks up, then dies down again.

fields.Title: Feld "Insular" Console: "'Urgence -- Ouvert!' reads one dial..."
fields.Dialogue Text: 'Urgence -- Ouvert!' reads one dial key. 'Allumer', reads another. 'RadiodiffusÃ©', says the frequency band.

fields.Title: Half Light: "A sudden wave of anxiety makes your..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A sudden wave of anxiety makes your skin crawl.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno knows. This place is spooky a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno knows. This place is spooky as fuck."

fields.Title: Reaction Speed: "Of course. Anything else you want w..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Of course. Anything else you want with this console?

fields.Title: You: ""Failing that we could... go back t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Failing that we could... go back to the mainland and get some from..."

fields.Title: Feld "Insular" Console: "The console looks on as you talk, m..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The console looks on as you talk, mute and unpowered. Its dials are covered in dust.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""The fuck is this...." He stares at..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "The fuck is this...." He stares at the dials: "'Urgence -- Ouvert!', 'Allumer', 'RadiodiffusÃ©'. Maybe, like, press the buttons or something."

fields.Title: Shivers: "No, it's more than that. There's so..."
fields.Dialogue Text: No, it's more than that. There's something there, waiting.

fields.Title: You: "Could this console open the blast d..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Could this console open the blast door?

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: Variable["seafort.blast_interfacing_open_big_one"]  or  (Variable["TASK.open_blast_door"]  and  Variable["TASK.open_blast_door_done"] == false)  or  Variable["TASK.fuel_the_generator_done"]

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""It's on..." He smiles. "Turn: Emer..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's on..." He smiles. "Turn: Emergency -- Open!"

fields.Title: Interfacing: "There are barrels all around. One o..."
fields.Dialogue Text: There are barrels all around. One of them must still have fuel in it... Pour it into a generator and voila!

fields.Title: You: ""Don't worry, I've got a gun. No bu..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Don't worry, I've got a gun. No bullets, but I have a gun."

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: Variable["seafort.console_cuno_spooky_place"]  and  CheckItem("bullet") == false  and  (CheckItem("gun_ruby") or  CheckItem("gun_villiers"))

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Are you?" He squints at you -- squ..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Are you?" He squints at you -- squints into your soul. "*Are you?*"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "Nothing happens. "We need to restor..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Nothing happens. "We need to restore power before using this, officer. There was a generator that you missed..." He looks upstairs. "It didn't look like there was fuel in it."
fields.Alternate1: Nothing happens. "We need to restore power before using this, officer. The generator..." He looks upstairs. "It didn't look like there was fuel in it."

fields.Title: Feld "Insular" Console: "Nothing happens as you turn the dia..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Nothing happens as you turn the dial. The power is off, the console stands silent.

fields.Title: Perception (Sight): "Pollen drifts in the light shaft."
fields.Dialogue Text: Pollen drifts in the light shaft.

fields.Title: You: ""I don't have a gun.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't have a gun."

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: Variable["seafort.console_kim_mentioned_gun"]  and  CheckItem("gun_ruby") == false  and  CheckItem("gun_villiers") == false

fields.Title: You: ""I also have a gun.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I also have a gun."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Then it's extra good that mine is..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Then it's extra good that mine is not."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I know. It was not easy to acquire.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I know. It was not easy to acquire."

fields.Title: Small Blast Door: "The door comes screeching to a halt..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The door comes screeching to a halt. Behind it you see a hole in the concrete wall, where light shines in.
fields.Alternate1: The door comes screeching to a halt. Behind it you see a hole in the concrete wall. A gust of wind blows in.

fields.Title: Shivers: "No, it's more than that. There's so..."
fields.Dialogue Text: No, it's more than that. There's something there, waiting.

fields.Title: Shivers: "No, it's more than that. There's so..."
fields.Dialogue Text: No, it's more than that. There's something there, waiting.

fields.Title: Feld "Insular" Console: "The keys rattle like teeth as black..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The keys rattle like teeth as black dust rises from them. This must be the console of some antique computation device. The wires from the generator upstairs are routed into its innards.
fields.Alternate1: A rattling sound, like teeth... the keyboard hasn't been functional in decades. This must be the console of another radiocomputer, albeit a much, much older model. The wires from the generator upstairs are routed into its innards.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Possibly..." He inspects the dials..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Possibly..." He inspects the dials. "'Urgence -- Ouvert!', 'Allumer', 'RadiodiffusÃ©'. It sounds like this device was used to control the electronics here. Maybe it still does?"

fields.Title: You: "No. It's too far fetched."
fields.Dialogue Text: No. It's too far fetched.

fields.Title: Feld "Insular" Console: "Nothing happens."
fields.Dialogue Text: Nothing happens.

fields.Title: Feld "Insular" Console: "The dial slides under the glass, da..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The dial slides under the glass, dark and silent. Restoring electric power has not breathed life into it.

fields.Title: You: ""What if we get into another fight?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What if we get into another fight?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Who the fuck is Soona?" he grunts...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Who the fuck is Soona?" he grunts. "Never mind. It won't work. This is fucking... military mega-grade shit, you know? It's also, like, four hundred years old."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Fucking great news, cop. Scare awa..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Fucking great news, cop. Scare away whatever shit out there's gonna spook on us with an *empty fucking gun*."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""It's sweet you got government fuel..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's sweet you got government fuel -- way sweet -- but there ain't shit left in there. You need, like, a full load. Let's check outside when you're done with this."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""But, officer," he looks you in the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "But, officer," he looks you in the eye, "then we would have to *swim* back to the mainland. Let's just look around, okay."

fields.Title: Small Blast Door: "The blast door opens with a series..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The blast door opens with a series of clicks. A shaft of light appears, then widens, as the light shines in.
fields.Alternate1: The blast door opens with a series of clicks. A cold wind blows in -- you see darkness behind it...

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Fuckin' right!" Cuno points to the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Fuckin' right!" Cuno points to the opening.

fields.Title: Interfacing: "It's on! Automatic boot. Now, just..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It's on! Automatic boot. Now, just turn the key...

fields.Title: You: "Run your fingers across the keyboar..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Run your fingers across the keyboard.

fields.Title: Feld "Insular" Console: "The lighting in the room turns on w..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The lighting in the room turns on with a sizzle. A dim, ambient orange.

fields.Title: Hand/Eye Coordination: "Harry, this reminds you -- you're o..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Harry, this reminds you -- you're out of bullets.

fields.Title: You: ""What's there?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What's there?"

fields.Title: Reaction Speed: "What about the fuel you found in th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: What about the fuel you found in the MC? The red government-marked fuel...

fields.Title: Reaction Speed: "Yeah, okay. There's barely anything..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Yeah, okay. There's barely anything left in there. You have to find a larger supply.

fields.Title: Feld "Insular" Console: "The dial slides under the glass, si..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The dial slides under the glass, silently. You make out defunct stations on the UKV frequency. The words "FELD INSULAR" are written on the band.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Try fucking with that one. It's re..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Try fucking with that one. It's red." He points to the emergency dial switch. It is large and alarmingly red.

fields.Title: You: ""Before -- outside. When we were wa..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Before -- outside. When we were walking across the sand, I felt someone watching me."

fields.Title: Feld "Insular" Console: "The console stands by, mutely. 'Urg..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The console stands by, mutely. 'Urgence -- Ouvert!' reads a dial key. 'Allumer,' reads another. The frequency band says: 'RadiodiffusÃ©.'

fields.Title: You: "What is this? (Run your fingers acr..."
fields.Dialogue Text: What is this? (Run your fingers across the keyboard.)

fields.Title: Logic: "An *idea* lights up in your head..."
fields.Dialogue Text: An *idea* lights up in your head...

fields.Title: You: ""Before -- outside. When we were wa..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Before -- outside. When we were walking across the sand, I felt someone watching me."

fields.Title: You: ""My gun is out of bullets, by the w..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "My gun is out of bullets, by the way."

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: Variable["seafort.console_kim_mentioned_gun"]  and  CheckItem("bullet") == false  and  (CheckItem("gun_ruby") or  CheckItem("gun_villiers"))

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno isn't a machine-meister." He..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno isn't a machine-meister." He stares at the dials. "'Urgence -- Ouvert!', 'Allumer', 'RadiodiffusÃ©'.... Yeah, why the fuck not?"

fields.Title: You: ""Don't worry kid. I'm a good guy wi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Don't worry kid. I'm a good guy with a gun."

fields.Title: You: "Turn: 'Emergency -- Open!'"
fields.Dialogue Text: Turn: 'Emergency -- Open!'

fields.Title: You: ""Wait, what about this fuel I found..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Wait, what about this fuel I found from my MC?" (Show him the canister.)

fields.Title: You: "Push: 'Light (Interior)'."
fields.Dialogue Text: Push: 'Light (Interior)'.

fields.Title: Feld "Insular" Console: "The console is powered off and cove..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The console is powered off and covered in dust. 'Urgence -- Ouvert!' reads a dial key. 'Allumer', reads another. The frequency band says: 'RadiodiffusÃ©'.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno's gonna stop you right there...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno's gonna stop you right there. This..." he strokes the console, "ain't gonna work." He points upward, to the generator. "Not without the juice. You gotta fuel that shit if you want it to work. Let's look outside maybe?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""We should look around outside. The..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "We should look around outside. There are barrels all over, maybe one of them still has something in it..." He looks into the dim light to his right.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""We're better off looking for a mec..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "We're better off looking for a mechanical solution -- if we need one at all."

fields.Title: You: ""Or we could get some from the boat..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Or we could get some from the boat engine?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""My Kineema?" He shakes his head. "..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "My Kineema?" He shakes his head. "I don't want to do that. Let's just look around."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""After you." The lieutenant gesture..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "After you." The lieutenant gestures at the opening.

fields.Title: Small Blast Door: "The door comes screeching to a halt..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The door comes screeching to a halt. Behind it you see a hole in the concrete wall, where light shines in.
fields.Alternate1: The door comes screeching to a halt. Behind it you see a hole in the concrete wall. A gust of wind blows in.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""The console of an antique computat..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "The console of an antique computation device." The lieutenant points to the wires running into the machine. "The generator upstairs, with wires coming out. They terminate here."

fields.Title: You: "Turn: 'Emergency -- Open!'"
fields.Dialogue Text: Turn: 'Emergency -- Open!'

fields.Title: You: "Slide: 'Radio' dial."
fields.Dialogue Text: Slide: 'Radio' dial.

fields.Title: You: ""Are you sure?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Are you sure?"

fields.Title: Feld "Insular" Console: "The old button is stuck."
fields.Dialogue Text: The old button is stuck.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Don't worry. I have a gun." He tak..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Don't worry. I have a gun." He takes out his sidearm, checks the barrel, then holsters it again.

fields.Title: You: ""There was something I needed to do..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "There was something I needed to do with this console first..."
